snippet.textDisplay: So many videos at BA (all of which I adore) where the chefs are handling hot food with nitrile gloves and burning their hands have resulted in my need to comment. It has probably been mentioned in comments before but wearing a light pair of cotton gloves under the nitrile gloves allows for much easier handling of hot foods. All I could think about during this episode is that Claire might have been able to get more folds in if it had been more manageable to handle by wearing those cotton gloves under the nitrile. I know that’s what I do and is popular in the BBQ/grilling community. Either way I adore everything BATK, but just had to comment about this glove and burning fingers situation.
